{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, we will improve our sign recognition algorithm with sign videos captured from various camera angles.",
    "Expanding our database with recordings from diverse angles with different cameras not only increases the size of our database but also diversifies the data used to train our models for accurate recognition.",
    "In addition, the current APP version cannot recognise the continuous emergence of new signs.",
    "To this end, we are dedicated to timely updating our database.Our APP primarily serves Auslan users, with a focus on specialised educational functions within family units.",
    "However, our APP can be seamlessly migrated to support other sign languages, such as American Sign Language (ASL), British Sign Language (BSL), and Chinese Sign Language (CSL)."
  ]
}